data.text: @DJtheHRLady @Caitlyn_Jenner Donna, I’m so grateful for your willingness to engage in the conversation. The ability to put aside our differences & listen for understanding is something that so many of us need & you did that!

@DJtheHRLady @Caitlyn_Jenner My friend, you did fantastic!! Open minds and hearts were everywhere today. It was on honor to hear your conversation. Thanks @Caitlyn_Jenner and @hutchinsophia for joining us! #BeYou #AreYouWithUs
